    <h3>Community Information</h3>
    <p>Culture and spirit is what makes the city of Green Bay stand out. The City made famous by the NFL's Green Bay Packers, the smallest American market to have a professional team and a recent Super Bowl winner, has a lot more to offer than just football. Striking museums and cultural events like the city lighting ceremonies, parades, marathons, food festivals, and concerts strive to show off the diverse activities this town has to offer. If you have always wanted to experience the excitement snow has to offer or you are just looking to fulfill your wintertime adrenaline rush, then this city is for you. Cold winters allow for several fun outdoor activities including skiing, snowboarding, sledding, snowmobiling, and mountain climbing.
</p>
